44-5432.Ensuring Transparency in Prior Authorization Act, how cited.

Sections 44-5432 to 44-5444 shall be known and may be cited as the Ensuring Transparency in Prior Authorization Act.

SourceLaws 2025, LB77, ยง 1.Operative Date: January 1, 2026
